It not only prevents damage, but also gives your customers and employees confidence in the safety of your business environment. This is how the MCZ subsidy helps your company. The government offers financial support with [the MCZ subsidy](https://www.rvo.nl/subsidies-financing/mcz). With this scheme you receive a 50% discount on cybersecurity investments, up to a maximum of €1,250. This allows you to take a maximum of €2,500 in security measures. An ideal step to strengthen your digital security. This subsidy is specifically intended for new investments, such as:
securing your network and WiFi;
setting up two-factor authentication;
implementing backup systems;
offering cyber awareness training for your team.

Our collaboration with recognized cybersecurity specialists, such as Threadstone, not only provides you with the right tools, but also the insights and guidance you need to keep your business secure. With our SME solution you get:
an extensive risk inventory of your digital vulnerabilities;
training for your team to recognize and prevent cyber risks;
monitoring and detection to actively identify threats. This way you are not only prepared for the dangers of today, but also for the challenges of tomorrow.
